\Lambda_{\mu'}^{\mu}\Lambda_{\nu'}^{\nu}g_{\mu\nu} & =g_{\mu'\nu'}\nonumber \\
\Rightarrow\qquad\left(\det\left(\Lambda\right)\right)^{2} & =1\nonumber \\
\det\left(\Lambda\right) & =\pm1
\end{align}

\end_inset

Für 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu'=0=\nu'$
\end_inset

